<br>
And then chaining has to be learned again and again on every mob you encounter, because the timing is different on many mobs. Fast hitting vs slow hitting. Caster mobs vs non-caster mobs. Mobs with procs vs mobs with no procs.<br>
<br>
Happy training. And if you ever join a mage group they will have way more respect for you if you can chain and thus make the whole group more powerfull.<br>
<br>
Regards,<br>
