<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Earth is probably the best pet to learn this skill on as the root effect can buy you some time to get away if you mess up.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
I disagree.  No reason to practice this skill on the battlefield where you can die if you screw it up.<br>
<br>
Here's how you practice:<br>
1) Go to GFay<br>
2) Memorize any lvl 4 pet<br>
3) Summon the pet<br>
4) Summon another pet and issue the /pet get lost command just before the spell completes.<br>
<br>
You should have a new pet standing at your side and should not have seen the &quot;You are only allowed one pet at a time&quot; message.<br>
<br>
There, you've succesfully practiced chaining pets at absolutely zero risk to yourself <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dabrighter2>Dabrighter2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 101<br> <font color=#333333>(1/24/03 9:53:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8547.topic&index=37>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Am I doomed if I can't Chain cast pets?</span><hr size=1> Learn things everyday.  Thanks.  I did not know you could start a macro from the macro window in mid-cast.  {I use my hot keys for just about everything.  I always moved my macros to a hot-key and used them from there. } <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#333333>- </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower>The Magician's Tower</a><font color=#333333> - </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral>General</a> <font color=#333333> - </font><a href="http://www.magecompendium.com/">The Mage Compendium</a><font color=#333333> - </font>  <br><br><table border=0 align=center><tr><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">Upgrade your account to ezSupporter...</a></td><td><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/spacer.gif" width=15 height=1 border=0></td><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">...and never see another ad or pop-up again</a></td></tr></table><CENTER><!-- START BOTTOM AD SCRIPT -->
